## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in the selected articles. The analysis primarily relies on English-language sources, which may not fully capture the global perspective on media distrust. Additionally, the focus on recent publications may overlook historical nuances that contribute to the current state of media skepticism among Republicans.